{"tid":389106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到仆街】【公屋DIY】偷位改造露台戶主：有咩問題？！","createTime":"2017-09-06T03:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T06:12:11.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06d6030fc6e98935f1186438ea2fec34a24c43b8","tid":389106,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170906/2_545761_0/-%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8BDIY-%E5%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E9%9C%B2%E5%8F%B0-%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%BB-%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170906%2F2_545761_0%2F-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258BDIY-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2580%25A0%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%25A9%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-&d=E2yCoEQOH8xopYD9uxQ%2FpqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=b491ea3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170906%2F2_545761_0%2F-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258BDIY-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2580%25A0%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%25A9%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-&h=1cd89fe5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170906/2_545761_0/-%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8BDIY-%E5%81%B7%E4%BD%8D%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E9%9C%B2%E5%8F%B0-%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%BB-%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-</a><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山耀安邨於1988年落成，是馬鞍山新市鎮第二個入伙的公屋屋邨，亦是最早參與租者置其屋計劃的公共屋邨之一，可租可買。近日，有市民發現耀安邨耀榮樓一低層單位，涉嫌偷位，把原來的花槽位、窗台位改造，加上鐵欄，看上去儼如一個小露台。本刊查問得知該單位已被買入，屬私人物業。記者拍門求證，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戶主表現不耐煩，反問記者一句：「有什麼問題？大驚小怪！」</span>但到底如此改裝有沒有問題？ <br />\n<br />\n租客方面，租務部職員表示，「是租戶的話，房屋署一定不容許這樣改裝，如是業主，我們就監管不了。其實這樣改裝都要和管業處申請，視乎管業處批准與否，但租戶一定不可改裝。」業主方面，管業處職員回覆查詢，指上述兩個單位正被管業處出律師信告。「如果他們不拆的話，會被釘契。」他補充，即是購入單位，成為業主都不可擅自改裝。<span style=\"color: red;\">「因為這屬於外牆的結構，屋宇署有規定不可以加任何東西。」 </span><br />\n<br />\n覺得無問題 有本事咪改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e5b21f2796fb5949f4bf40924f8af13b527e96","tid":389106,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得無問題 有本事咪改</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至多釘契<br />\n<br />\n佢唔賣既話, 真係無乜符"},{"pid":"e73a16c0587e236fb981ec4c6b4e2545c7639959","tid":389106,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"人地平到喊買入，住一世，你無佢乎"},{"pid":"5abc626b705f053c3f16b320a71c029d6e9bf5b0","tid":389106,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"有什麼問題？大驚小怪！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7639b0bd73bbe3130f6c781bb8fac7a21bc5697","tid":389106,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:47:00.000Z","msg":"釘契真係無乜用"},{"pid":"1b9526af92f0ff36427d71de861fe9965f5a116f","tid":389106,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"大把人把窗台位改成儲物位啦"},{"pid":"81881bce6976e154937852c01f7fe34625b131be","tid":389106,"uid":45672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"買左既公屋都自住多。話之你啦。不過佢整埋落地玻璃又真係幾靚"},{"pid":"0c8cab6c40553c9b479c0db5c9459aac928cc747","tid":389106,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"好多人買左之後都係亂改<br />\n唔撚理房署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713c21f1a291735b74557a1f3430467dd76f59e7","tid":389106,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"呢個改裝有